See a problem?
Let us know!


  
  
            Established in 1992, Ashmore Investment Management Limited is one of the leading investment management companies in the world. Headquartered in the United Kingdom, it deals in various investment themes, including dollar debt, local currency, corporate high yield, equity and special situations. The company offers its services through structured products and variable proportion portfolio protection structures. The company employs a portfolio management and research team that specializes in areas, including research, business development, client relations and operations. Ashmore Investment Management Limited s distribution partners include private banks, brokers and wealth managers who distribute the company s funds on a private placement basis.
          






















